<i>noun</i>: 약혼자 [야콘자], 약혼녀 [야콘녀] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>약혼자 [야콘자]</dt><br>
<dd>fiance; fiancee; the engaged person</dd><br>
<dd>결혼을 하기로 약속한 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who one has promised to marry.</dd><br>
<dt>약혼녀 [야콘녀]</dt><br>
<dd>fiancee; bride-to-be</dd><br>
<dd>결혼을 하기로 약속한 여자.</dd><br>
<dd>A woman that one has promised to marry.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>